page.title: 18WILDLIFE IN FERNESS
page.content: FOREST- tawny owl, capercaillie, wood- pecker, wood pigeon, crossbill, woodcock, badger, roe deer, red squirrel, wildcat, fox. MOOR- short-eared owl, pheasant, golden eagle, grouse, sparrowhawk, hen harrier, buzzard, kestrel, cuckoo mountain hare, fox FARMLAND- crow, gulls, rook, magpie, jackdaw, rabbit, mouse, weasel, stoat, mole. VILLAGE AND GARDEN- thrush, blackbird, swallow, swift, finches, redwing, blue-tit, great tit, coal tit, house sparrow, robin, yellow-hammer, frog, toad, newt, vole. RIVER- osprey, heron, dipper, salmon, trout, stickleback, otter, water rat.
